    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p>Released on September 14, 2020, the <a href=\"https://www.funraise.org/giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2020 Global Trends in Giving Report</strong></a> examines how donors prefer to give and engage with their favorite causes and charitable organizations.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.funraise.org/giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-27204 size-large\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020-Giving-Report-Promo-Graphic-2-1024x512.png?resize=960%2C480\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020-Giving-Report-Promo-Graphic-2.png?resize=1024%2C512&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020-Giving-Report-Promo-Graphic-2.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020-Giving-Report-Promo-Graphic-2.png?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020-Giving-Report-Promo-Graphic-2.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h3><strong>In Italian</strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://italianonprofit.it/global-trends-in-giving-2020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2020 Global Trends in Giving Focus Italia</a></strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Previous Editions</strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-GivingReport-English.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 Global Trends in Giving Report</a><br />\n</strong><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-GivingReport-Spanish.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 Informe sobre tendencias globales de donaci\u00f3n</a></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-GivingReport-Portuguese.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2018 Relat\u00f3rio Tend\u00eancias Globais de Doa\u00e7\u00f5es</strong></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-GivingReport-French.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2018 rapport sur les tendances mondiales en mati\u00e8re de dons</strong></a></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-Global-Trends-in-Giving-Report-English-Final.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 Global Trends in Giving Report</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2017-Global-Trends-in-Giving-Report-Spanish-Final.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 Informe sobre tendencias globales de donaci\u00f3n</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2017-Global-Trends-in-Giving-Report-French-Final.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 rapport sur les tendances mondiales en mati\u00e8re de dons</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Related Research</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/global-ngo-technology-report/\"><strong>The Global NGO Technology Report</strong></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project/\"><strong>The Open Data Project</strong></a></p>\n",
